item.skttrans: Ar+ya b+ha ga wa ti b+he sha tsa gu ru bai Dur+ya bra pa se phurpa da prad ni po phul l+ya nA ma ma hA yA na su tra
item.coloph: 'phags pa bcom ldan 'das sman gyi bla bai DUr+ya'i 'od kyi sngon gyi smon lam rgyas pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs s+h+yo// //rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang / dA na shI la dang / zhu chen gyi lots+tsha ba ban+de ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te skad gsar bcad kyis bcos nas gtan la phab pa
